基本設計概念: Solve a pre-determined set of problems Memorize solutions to all subproblems Unique Path走到(i, j)的位置，只有可能來自上面或左邊令$P(i, j)$表示走到(i, j)位置的方法數 $$P(i, j) =  egin{cases}1 &amp; 	ext{ if } i=0 
ewline1 &amp; 	ext{ if } j=0 
ewlineP(i-1, j) + P(i, j-1) &amp; 	ext{ if } i \geq 1, j \geq 1\end{cases}$$ 又稱為state equation 62. Unique Paths 1int uniquePaths(int m, int n) {2 // create a m*n matrix3 vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt; P(m);4 for(int i = 0; i &lt; m; ++i) P[i].resize(n);56 // init7 for(int j = 0; j &lt; n; ++j) 8 P[0][j] = 1;9 10 for(int i = 0; i &lt; m; ++i) 11 P[i][0] = 1;12 1314 // update15 for(int i = 1; i &lt; m; ++i) 16 for(int j = 1; j &lt; n; ++j) 17 P[i][j] = P[i - 1][j] + P[i][j - 1];1819 20 return P[m - 1][n - 1];21} 時間複雜度: $O(mn)$ Max subsequence sum給予$\left [ a_{1}, a_{2}, \dots , a_{n} ight ]$ 求連續子序列之和的最大值$Max_{i,j} = a_i +a_{i+1} + \dots + a_{j}$ Subproblem: $R_i$為$\left [ a_1, a_2, \dots, a_i ight ]$的最大子序列之和 $M_i$代表目前的子序列和最大值 Init:$R_1 = a_1$$M_1 = a_1$ $$R_i = max  egin{cases}R_{i-1} + a_i &amp; 
ewlinea_i &amp;\end{cases}$$ $$M_i = max  egin{cases}M_{i-1} &amp; 
ewlineR_i &amp;\end{cases}$$ 53. Maximum Subarray 1int maxSubArray(vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; nums) {2 const int len = nums.size();3 vector&lt;int&gt; M(len); // max subseq so far4 vector&lt;int&gt; R(len); // R[i] means max subseq (contain ai)56 // init7 M[0] = R[0] = nums[0];89 // update10 for(int i = 1; i &lt; len; ++i) {11 R[i] = max(R[i - 1] + nums[i], nums[i]);12 M[i] = max(M[i - 1], R[i]);13 }1415 return M[len - 1];16} 時間複雜度: $O(n)$ Optimal Investment&emsp; Suppose there are $m$ different money investment plans $P_1, P_2,…, P_m$ available, Plan $P_i$ takes $y_i$ years and will increase your money by a factor of $(1+r_i)^{y_i}$. (In other words, if you invest $D$ dollars in plan $P_i$, after $y_i$ years, you will have $D(1+r_i)^{y_i}$ dollars.) For every $i$, $y_i$ is a positive integer and $r_i \geq 0$. &emsp; You start with some fixed amount of money $M$ and need to choose a series of plans to invest one by one. You must invest all your money into a single plan at any given time. You must select some plans with the total duration at most $n$ years. The goal is to maximize your money at the end of these investments. The series of plans you choose may include the same plan any number of times. Assume that the annual interest rate $r_i$ satisfies $r_1 \geq r_2 \geq … \geq r_m$ Design an $O(mn)$-time algorithm which finds the final amount of money after the optimal series of investment. 共$n$年，有$m$個plan可選擇 Subproblem: 令$C(i, j)$為max profit，代表只用了$P_1, P_2,…,P_i$的投資組合於$j$年之間，目前狀態下只需考慮要不要不投資$P_i$ $C(i,j) = max  egin{cases}C(i-1 , j) &amp; 	ext{, don’t invest } P_i 
ewlineC(i, j-y_i) \cdot (1+r_i)^{y_i} &amp; 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ at least once}\end{cases}$ Algo: 為維持可讀性，先不管陣列超出邊界存取問題因為沒有限定一個plan能投資幾次，所以固定$i$個plan，$1 \sim n$年都有可能再選擇$P_i$ $	ext{for }i = 1 	ext{ to }m 	ext{ plans} \ \space \space \space \space 	ext{for }j = 1 	ext{ to } n 	ext{ years} \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space C(i,j) = max  egin{cases} C(i-1 , j) & 	ext{, don't invest } P_i \ C(i, j-y_i) \cdot (1+r_i)^{y_i} & 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ at least once} \end{cases} \ 	ext{output: }C(m,n)$ Adding an extra restriction that each plan can only be invested at most twice, Also, you are limited to choosing series of at most $t$ plans (Investing in the same plan twice counts as two). Design a polynomial time algorithm which finds the optimal set of plans. Any algorithm which runs in time polynomial in $mnt$ suffices. Subproblem: 令$C(i,j,k)$為max profit，代表 使用$P_1, P_2, \dots, P_i$ 投資$\leq j$年 共使用了$\leq k$個plan $C(i,j,k) = max  egin{cases} C(i-1 , j,k) &amp; 	ext{, don’t invest } P_i 
ewline C(i-1, j-y_i, k-1) \cdot (1+r_i)^{y_i} &amp; 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ once} 
ewline C(i-1, j-2y_i, k-2) \cdot (1+r_i)^{2y_i} &amp; 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ twice} \end{cases}$ Algo: $	ext{for }i = 1 	ext{ to }m 	ext{ plans} \ \space \space \space \space 	ext{for }j = 1 	ext{ to } n 	ext{ years} \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space 	ext{for }k = 1 	ext{ to }t 	ext{ plans used} \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space C(i,j,k) = max  egin{cases} C(i-1 , j,k) & 	ext{, don't invest } P_i \ C(i-1, j-y_i, k-1) \cdot (1+r_i)^{y_i} & 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ once} \ C(i-1, j-2y_i, k-2) \cdot (1+r_i)^{2y_i} & 	ext{, invest } P_i 	ext{ twice} \end{cases} \ 	ext{output: }C(m,n,t)$ Trip Planning一個旅途$[0, 1, 2, …, n]$，每1km有休息區 起點為$0$ 停在第$i$點的住宿費為$C_i$ 每天只走20km以內 想求得 $0$走到$n$的最小花費 整個旅途中住過哪些休息區 Solution 最後停在$n$，所以必要支出$C_n$ Subproblem: $A[i]$表示可走到$i$的最小花費 紀錄路徑於$B_i$，表示到達$A_i$之前的位置(第$i$公里) init: 前1~20公里最省錢方法就是直接一開始直接到達，B則全部初始化為0 $A[1,2, \dots ,20] = C[1,2, \dots ,20]$ $B[i] = 0 	ext{ , where } i = 0 \sim n$ Algo: $	ext{for i = 21 to n} \ \space \space A \left [ i ight ] = min(A \left [ i - 20 ight ], A \left [ i - 19 ight ],...,A \left [ i - 1 ight ]) + C_i \ \space \space B \left [i ight ] = j 	ext{ , if the above min pick } A \left [ j ight ]$ Resturant DP Groups: $G_1, G_2, \dots , G_m$ number of people: $a_1, a_2, \dots , a_m$ dollars per person: $d_1, d_2, \dots , d_m$ Want: $Max \sum_{S} a_{i}d_{i}$ , subject to $\sum_{S} a_{i} \leq n$ Subproblem: $S(j,k)$ : $Max \sum_{S} a_{i}d_{i} 	ext{, subject to }  egin{cases} \sum_{S}a_{i} & 
ewline S \subseteq \left \{ G_1, G_2, \dots, G_{j} ight \} & \end{cases}$ $T(j,k)$ : set of groups selected in $S(j,k)$ $S(j,k) = max  egin{cases} S(j-1,k- a_j) + a_{j}d_{j} &amp; (	ext{ accept }G_{j}) 
ewline S(j-1, k) &amp; (	ext{ don’t accept }G_{j}) \end{cases}$ $T(j,k) =  egin{cases} 0 & 	ext{ if } T(j-1,k-a_{j}) \cup \left \{ G_{j} ight \} (	ext{ accept }G_{j}) 
ewline 1 & 	ext{ if } S(j-1, k) (	ext{ don't accept }G_{j}) \end{cases}$ Algo: $	ext{for } j = 1 	ext{ to } m \ \space \space \space \space 	ext{for }k = 1 	ext{ to }n \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space S(j,k) = max  egin{cases} S(j-1,k- a_j) + a_{j}d_{j} & (	ext{ accept }G_{j}) \ S(j-1, k) & (	ext{ don't accept }G_{j}) \end{cases} \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space T(j,k) =  egin{cases} 0 & 	ext{ if } T(j-1,k-a_{j}) \cup \left \{ G_{j} ight \} (	ext{ accept }G_{j}) \ 1 & 	ext{ if } S(j-1, k) (	ext{ don't accept }G_{j}) \end{cases} \ 	ext{output: }S(m,n), T(m,n)$ Time Complexity: $O(mn)$ Space: $S(j,k)$: $\Theta (mn)$ $T(j,k)$: $\Theta (m^{2}n)$ Sequence AlignmentAn application of biology, find the similarity of 2 DNA sequence. Input: X: $ACAAT$ Y: $AGATG$ Let mismatch costs $C_1$, gap costs $C_2$ Output: min cost ex. $ACAAT$ $AGATG$ $\Rightarrow$ 3 mismatch $ACAAT	ext{ _ }$$AGA	ext{ _ }TG$ $\Rightarrow$ 1 mismatch, 2 gaps $ACAAT	ext{ _ _ _ _ }$$A	ext{ _ _ _ _ }GATG$ $\Rightarrow$ 8 gaps Subproblem: $P(i, j)$: min cost of matching “first $i$ symbols of $X$” and “first $j$ symbols of $Y$” ex.$P(3,3)$: min cost of matching $ACA$ and $AGA$$P(1,5)$: min cost of matching $A$ and $ACTAG$ case 1: match $X[i]$ with $Y[i]$ case 2: match $X[i]$ with gap case 3: match $Y[i]$ with gap Subproblem: $P(i,j) = min  egin{cases} P(i-1, j-1) +  egin{cases} C_1 &amp; 	ext{ if } X[i] 
eq Y[j] 
ewline 0 &amp; 	ext{ else} \end{cases} &amp; 	ext{ case1 } 
ewline P(i-1, j) + C_2 &amp; 	ext{ case2 } 
ewline P(i, j-1) + C_2 &amp; 	ext{ case3 } \end{cases}$$B(i, j)$: record the cases choosed at $i,j$ Init: match X with an empty Y: $P[i,0] = C_{2}i$ match Y with an empty X: $P[0,j] = C_{2}j$ Algo: $	ext{for } i = 0 	ext{ to } m \ \space \space \space \space 	ext{for } j = 0 	ext{ to } n \ \space \space \space \space \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space P(i,j) = min  egin{cases} P(i-1, j-1) +  egin{cases} C_1 & 	ext{ if } X[i] 
eq Y[j] \ 0 & 	ext{ else} \end{cases} & 	ext{ case1 } \ P(i-1, j) + C_2 & 	ext{ case2 } \ P(i, j-1) + C_2 & 	ext{ case3 } \end{cases} \ \space \space \space \space \space \space \space \space B(i,j) =  egin{cases} 1 & 	ext{ if choose caes 1 } \ 2 & 	ext{ if choose caes 2 } \ 3 & 	ext{ if choose caes 3 } \end{cases} \ 	ext{output: }P(m,n)$ Checking $B(m,n)$, we can get the min cost alignment of $X,Y$ $	ext{if } B(m,n) = 1 \ \space \space 	ext{match } X[m] 	ext{ with } Y[n] \ \space \space 	ext{check } B(m-1,n-1) 	ext{ ...etc} \ 	ext{if } B(m,n) = 2 \ \space \space 	ext{match } X[m] 	ext{ with } gap \ \space \space 	ext{check } B(m-1,n-1) 	ext{ ...etc} \ 	ext{if } B(m,n) = 3 \ \space \space 	ext{match } Y[n] 	ext{ with } gap \ \space \space 	ext{check } B(m-1,n-1) 	ext{ ...etc}$ at most $m+n$ check linear time complexity

HW41.分別針對不同Spreading Factor情況下LoRa在移動下（可騎承腳踏車、搭公車、搭捷運、搭貓纜）所傳送資料的狀況做記錄（例：Packet Error Rate） 頻率設定位置: setFrequency() in the file: Sketchbook\libraries\RadioHead\RH_RF95.cpp;Line 114: setFrequency(918.7); 1typedef enum2 {3 Bw125Cr45Sf128 = 0, ///&lt; Bw = 125 kHz, Cr = 4/5, Sf = 128chips/symbol, CRC on. Default medium range4 Bw500Cr45Sf128, ///&lt; Bw = 500 kHz, Cr = 4/5, Sf = 128chips/symbol, CRC on. Fast+short range5 Bw31_25Cr48Sf512, ///&lt; Bw = 31.25 kHz, Cr = 4/8, Sf = 512chips/symbol, CRC on. Slow+long range6 Bw125Cr48Sf4096, ///&lt; Bw = 125 kHz, Cr = 4/8, Sf = 4096chips/symbol, CRC on. Slow+long range7 } ModemConfigChoice; source codemyLoraServerSFtest-FieldTrailTx.ino 1#include &lt;SPI.h&gt;2#include &lt;RH_RF95.h&gt;34RH_RF95 rf95;56long counter=0;7void setup() { 8 Serial.begin(9600);9 delay(1000);10 while (!Serial) ; // Wait for serial port to be available11 if (!rf95.init())12 Serial.println("init failed"); 13 Serial.println();14 Serial.println("Lora init passed"); 15 16 rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr48Sf4096); // failed17 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr45Sf128); // test OK (Default medium range)18 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw500Cr45Sf128); // test OK (Fast + short range)19 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw31_25Cr48Sf512); // test OK (Slow + long range適用長距離)20 21 rf95.setTxPower(23, false);22}2324void loop() {25 counter++;26 String numString = "Server: "+ String(counter, DEC)+" "; //加空白以去除亂碼27 28 uint8_t data[14] = ""; 29 for (int i=0; i&lt;14; i++) {30 data[i] =numString[i]; // 31 } 32 rf95.send(data, sizeof(data));33 rf95.waitPacketSent();34 Serial.println(numString);35 delay(1000);36} myLoraClientSFtest-FieldTrailRx.ino 1#include &lt;SPI.h&gt;2#include &lt;RH_RF95.h&gt;3#include &lt;Wire.h&gt;4RH_RF95 rf95;5int counter=0;67void setup() 8{9 Serial.begin(9600);10 while (!Serial) ;11 if (!rf95.init())12 Serial.println("init failed");13 Serial.println("init passed"); 14 15 rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr48Sf4096); 16 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr45Sf128); 17 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw500Cr45Sf128); 18 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw31_25Cr48Sf512);19 rf95.setTxPower(23, false);20}2122void loop()23{24 25 if (rf95.available())26 { 27 uint8_t buf[14];28 uint8_t len = sizeof(buf);29 if (rf95.recv(buf, &amp;len))30 {31 counter++;32 Serial.print("Rx: ");33 Serial.println((char*)buf);34 Serial.print("RSSI: ");35 Serial.println(rf95.lastRssi(), DEC);36 }37 }38} 2.不同長度的展頻symbol數，會造成不同的傳送完成時間，請量測不同Spreading Factor傳送完成所需時間紀錄。source code1#include &lt;SPI.h&gt;2#include &lt;RH_RF95.h&gt;34RH_RF95 rf95;56long counter=0;7void setup() { 8 Serial.begin(9600);9 delay(1000);10 while (!Serial) ; // Wait for serial port to be available11 if (!rf95.init())12 Serial.println("init failed"); 13 Serial.println();14 Serial.println("Lora init passed"); 15 16 rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr48Sf4096); // failed17 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr45Sf128); // test OK (Default medium range)18 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw500Cr45Sf128); // test OK (Fast + short range)19 // rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw31_25Cr48Sf512); // test OK (Slow + long range適用長距離)20 21 rf95.setTxPower(23, false);22 23 //傳送1100筆資料24 for(int j = 0; j &lt;= 1100; j ++) {25 counter++;26 String numString = "Server: "+ String(counter, DEC)+" "; //加空白以去除亂碼27 28 uint8_t data[14] = ""; 29 for (int i=0; i&lt;14; i++) {30 data[i] =numString[i]; // 31 } 32 rf95.send(data, sizeof(data));33 rf95.waitPacketSent();34 Serial.println(numString);35 }36}3738void loop() {} RPi Serial monitor with timestamp 1import time2from pytz import timezone # pip install pytz3from datetime import datetime4import serial56ser = serial.Serial('/dev/ttyACM0', 9600)789while True:10 u = datetime.now(timezone('Asia/Taipei'))11 print(u.strftime('%H:%M:%S.%f')[:-3] + " &gt;&gt; " + ser.readline()) 使用樹莓派讀取serial好處是可以有準確的unix timestamp，只要有行動電源與手機(AP)就能到戶外進行實測，並直接將結果存成log.txt檔案放在RPi 參考 timestamp 樹莓派 https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10997577/python-timezone-conversion pytz-time-zones.py : https://gist.github.com/heyalexej/8bf688fd67d7199be4a1682b3eec7568 RadioHead API : https://www.airspayce.com/mikem/arduino/RadioHead/classRHGenericDriver.html#a0feda1f5522522dc50e0c26dcdef71dd HW5PM2.5 測試程式 1int dustPin=0; //A02float dustVal=0;3 4int delayTime=280;5int delayTime2=40;6float offTime=9680;78void setup(){9 Serial.begin(9600);10 pinMode(dustPin, INPUT);11}12 13void loop(){14 delayMicroseconds(delayTime);15 dustVal = analogRead(dustPin); 16 delayMicroseconds(delayTime2);17 delayMicroseconds(offTime);18 19 delay(1000);20 if (dustVal&gt;36.455)21 Serial.println((float(dustVal/1024)-0.0356)*120000*0.035);22} LoRa Client(TX) 傳輸PM2.5資料 1#include &lt;SPI.h&gt;2#include &lt;RH_RF95.h&gt;34RH_RF95 rf95;5int count = 0;67// PM2.58int dustPin=0; //A09float dustVal=0;10float AirQ;11String AirQT;1213void setup() { 14 Serial.begin(9600);15 pinMode(dustPin, INPUT);16 delay(1000);17 while (!Serial) ; // Wait for serial port to be available18 if (!rf95.init())19 Serial.println(&quot;init failed&quot;); 20 Serial.println();21 Serial.println(&quot;Lora init passed Bw31_25Cr48Sf512&quot; ); 2223 rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr45Sf128); // test OK (Default medium range)2425 26 rf95.setTxPower(23, false); 27 28}2930void loop() {31 count++;32 dustVal = analogRead(dustPin); 33 PM25Info(&amp;AirQ, &amp;AirQT);34 35 String numString = (String)count + &quot;,&quot; + (String)AirQ + &quot;,&quot; + AirQT + &quot; &quot;; //加空白以去除亂碼36 37 uint8_t data[14] = &quot;&quot;; 38 for (int i=0; i&lt;14; i++) {39 data[i] =numString[i]; // 40 } 41 rf95.send(data, sizeof(data));42 rf95.waitPacketSent();43 Serial.println(numString);4445 delay(1000);46}4748void PM25Info(float* aq, String* aqt) {49 if (dustVal&gt;36.455)50 *aq = float((dustVal/1024)-0.0356)*120000*0.035;515253 if (*aq &lt; 300) { *aqt=&quot; Good &quot;;}54 if (*aq &gt;= 300 &amp;&amp; *aq &lt; 1050) { *aqt=&quot; Moderate&quot;;}55 if (*aq &gt;= 1050 &amp;&amp; *aq &lt; 3000) { *aqt=&quot; Unhealthy&quot;;}56 if (*aq &gt; 3000) { *aqt=&quot; Hazardous&quot;;}57} LoRa Server(RX) 接收PM2.5資料 1#include &lt;SPI.h&gt;2#include &lt;RH_RF95.h&gt;3RH_RF95 rf95;456void setup() {7 Serial.begin(9600);8 while (!Serial) ;9 if (!rf95.init())10 Serial.println(&quot;init failed&quot;);11 Serial.println(&quot;init passed Bw125Cr45Sf128&quot;); 12 rf95.setModemConfig(RH_RF95::Bw125Cr45Sf128); 13 14 rf95.setTxPower(23, false);15}1617void loop(){18 if (rf95.available()) { 19 uint8_t buf[14];20 uint8_t len = sizeof(buf);21 if (rf95.recv(buf, &amp;len))22 {23 Serial.print(&quot;Rx: &quot;);24 Serial.println((char*)buf);25 Serial.print(&quot;RSSI: &quot;);26 Serial.println(rf95.lastRssi(), DEC);27 }28 }29} NodeRED 環境資料整合GatewayMQTT broker : rpi publisher: rpi subscriber: PC 由serial顯示LoRa Server(RX) 接收的PM2.5數值 解析payload並mqtt publishnodes: serial node:data switch function node(parse pm2.5): function node(parse rssi): mqtt node (pm2.5): mqtt node (RSSI): 接收topic: home/LoRa的subscriber程式1var mqtt = require('mqtt')2var client = mqtt.connect('mqtt://192.168.0.105') //broker ip (rpi)3var client2 = mqtt.connect('mqtt://192.168.0.105') 4 5client.on('connect', function () {6 console.log('mqtt broker connected!');7 client.subscribe('home/LoRa/pm2.5');8})9 10client.on('message', function (topic, msg) {11 let info = JSON.parse(msg)12 console.log('
